snippet.title: SWOOP
snippet.description:
I'm a filmmaker, vlogger, commentator, and recording artist ... I speak my mind, laugh a lot, and make movies about stories that move me. New films every week :) 

Official SWOOP MERCH is here!!!  
Grab it here:  http://bit.ly/swoopmerch

FAQ:
Q. do you edit your own films?  
A.  yes!

Q.  what camera do you use?
A.  you can see a complete list of the gear I use for my regular/weekly content linked down below in the "Gear I Use"  section

Q.  did you go to film school?
A.  no, I'm self taught.

Q.  what do you edit on?
A.  adobe premiere pro and after effects are my current go to-s

Q.  how do you write/plan/shoot your films
A.  i don't sleep hahaha
